<h4 class="quick-menu-exclude heading-anchor" data-content-chunk-id="f3dcc6b8-0353-4a5c-8723-056fc688aea9" id="ATitleMonsterStatBlocksVHrefHttpsWwwDndbeyondComCompendiumRulesBasicRulesMonsterStatBlocksVDataContentChunkIdC3d97af0D8594fceA64b8de387dbb84eMonsterStatBlocksVA"><a href="#ATitleMonsterStatBlocksVHrefHttpsWwwDndbeyondComCompendiumRulesBasicRulesMonsterStatBlocksVDataContentChunkIdC3d97af0D8594fceA64b8de387dbb84eMonsterStatBlocksVA" data-content-chunk-id="e090d41a-7ba8-4b1c-90f2-4f6c93afb63d"></a><a title="Monster Stat Blocks (V)" href="https://www.dndbeyond.com/compendium/rules/basic-rules/monster-stat-blocks-v" data-content-chunk-id="c3d97af0-d859-4fce-a64b-8de387dbb84e">Monster Stat Blocks (V)</a></h4>
