<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data-Last" data-content-chunk-id="4291a227-2afb-4040-99fa-09ee9e487202"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="bb1d5fa1-9e57-48d2-9195-40a3b718b720">Challenge</span>&nbsp;1/4 (50 XP)</p>
