<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="60943d9a-d430-4586-870b-820001974236"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="478ab7fc-a413-48d0-ab9b-45ddea69c9f1">Spellcasting.</span>&nbsp;The acolyte is a 1st-level spellcaster. Its spellcasting ability is Wisdom (spell save DC 12, +4 to hit with spell attacks). The acolyte has following cleric spells prepared:</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Hanging" data-content-chunk-id="b7d5ee5e-4c09-4400-a88b-feb61acc3a95">Cantrips (at will):&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="302fa860-3be7-48d4-81c0-a03c5bfc0611"><a class="tooltip-hover spell-tooltip" href="/spells/light" data-tooltip-href="/spells/2166-tooltip">light</a></span>,&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="fe6fd20e-14ca-4707-9fa7-589fb29aa3e5"><a class="tooltip-hover spell-tooltip" href="/spells/sacred-flame" data-tooltip-href="/spells/2236-tooltip">sacred flame</a></span>,&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="0cf9eb7f-7c02-4fb9-bec2-a6a3c0e5a649"><a class="tooltip-hover spell-tooltip" href="/spells/thaumaturgy" data-tooltip-href="/spells/2277-tooltip">thaumaturgy</a></span></p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Hanging" data-content-chunk-id="a3de72f1-0f63-4b66-b299-a769ba3639a6">1st level (3 slots):&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="dcc5286f-c7e5-42b1-b0d0-c708aa6cc699"><a class="tooltip-hover spell-tooltip" href="/spells/bless" data-tooltip-href="/spells/2016-tooltip">bless</a></span>,&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="892c3210-fb9a-4279-ab3c-65d0a195dbfc"><a class="tooltip-hover spell-tooltip" href="/spells/cure-wounds" data-tooltip-href="/spells/2056-tooltip">cure wounds</a></span>,&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="19be311e-1be4-43a6-a229-2e8c58c26eba"><a class="tooltip-hover spell-tooltip" href="/spells/sanctuary" data-tooltip-href="/spells/2237-tooltip">sanctuary</a></span></p>
