<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Hanging" data-content-chunk-id="7f62ed77-c8aa-436f-abe6-4b4f2be9faf4">2nd level (3 slots):&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="48222842-73fb-4f86-9716-c247d4891bc9"><a class="tooltip-hover spell-tooltip" href="/spells/detect-thoughts" data-tooltip-href="/spells/2067-tooltip">detect thoughts</a></span>,&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="0a392bd8-355e-4b28-9229-df3f82b9db53"><a class="tooltip-hover spell-tooltip" href="/spells/mirror-image" data-tooltip-href="/spells/2193-tooltip">mirror image</a></span>,&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="eae83036-f78e-489c-8ded-62f80173b6d6"><a class="tooltip-hover spell-tooltip" href="/spells/misty-step" data-tooltip-href="/spells/2195-tooltip">misty step</a></span></p>
