<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="b747d1e3-e7b3-4dcf-9733-db05789dd10f"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="66c9c027-0013-419d-bdeb-2e50ff0af799">Hit Points</span>&nbsp;33 (6d8 + 6)</p>
