<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Title" data-content-chunk-id="4c21af9b-65c3-4781-9f5a-204c0bb52a8c"><a class="tooltip-hover monster-tooltip" href="/monsters/16903-gladiator" data-tooltip-href="/monsters/16903-tooltip">Gladiator</a></p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Metadata" data-content-chunk-id="bfdcf976-17c7-4645-acea-9e0e3bf9efbb">Medium humanoid (any race), any alignment</p>
