<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="e68ea8d6-2794-44ef-9e51-18cc154f82f2"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="1a2a155d-babc-407f-bb05-cc52c086b0f2">Hit Points</span>&nbsp;112 (15d8 + 45)</p>
