<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="194c7e39-7d34-44ab-bd52-f5a3aaa7f676"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="ba0531f0-87c0-4ca0-953c-622ad84db7a3">Senses</span>&nbsp;passive Perception 12</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="1937537b-e58b-4410-a961-772749abbc61"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="828782b2-df79-4016-953e-09575577e33d">Languages</span>&nbsp;any one language (usually Common)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data-Last" data-content-chunk-id="733ba4e6-6e59-420c-9951-aa071f5b09a1"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="c58064ee-b5d1-4a94-8d40-b3d63efa8ac3">Challenge</span>&nbsp;1/8 (25 XP)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Heading--after-last-bar-" data-content-chunk-id="82a6a058-1444-45f2-80d0-013b4ca2deb1">Actions</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="bdd568d1-e992-42e3-9c1c-f9a01e3569ec"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="9ae58b52-7733-4b52-ba75-900814e95168">Spear.&nbsp;</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="d41021db-577b-4f35-95f8-3542b7bbe221">Melee or Ranged Weapon Attack:</span>&nbsp;+3 to hit, reach 5 ft. or range 20/60 ft., one target.<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="1fecc698-ea29-4d34-a497-4fce709eb928">&nbsp;Hit:</span>&nbsp;4 (1d6 + 1) piercing damage.</p>
</div>
<p class="Core-Styles_Core-Body-Last--to-apply-extra-space-" data-content-chunk-id="fc0693e3-b48b-47b3-b4e4-5968c60979bc"><span class="Serif-Character-Style_Bold-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="4487dd64-37d7-4684-a732-9cf99d8f3052">Guards</span>&nbsp;include members of a city watch, sentries in a citadel or fortified town, and the bodyguards of merchants and nobles.</p>
<div class="Basic-Text-Frame" data-content-chunk-id="8adf038e-2569-469f-a47f-d6c098c1e868">
