<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="e116550a-1073-408e-acb3-99d62709f37b"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="f4a15973-f5bb-4da6-ab88-4adf0554b474">Hit Points</span>&nbsp;52 (8d8 + 16)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="381c2aee-79d4-45f8-a3ff-3e78c705f05a"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="4d0faad0-9b5e-4511-bcf1-152fdf545601">Speed</span>&nbsp;30 ft.</p>
