<p class="Core-Styles_Core-Body-Last--to-apply-extra-space-" data-content-chunk-id="7a98665d-dd6a-47c9-a39d-6b3f63ce0886"><span class="Serif-Character-Style_Bold-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="0b08af6c-f215-463e-83a6-a87dc86cbfe5">Mages</span>&nbsp;spend their lives in the study and practice of magic. Good-aligned mages offer counsel to nobles and others in power, while evil mages dwell in isolated sites to perform unspeakable experiments without interference.</p>
