<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="45e74581-0970-4c16-b1f4-ae9f0742b034"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="a9620d27-44a4-422c-b100-0fc1f55b2823">Hit Points</span>&nbsp;27 (5d8 + 5)</p>
