<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="074dd50e-9973-4e56-a051-8699eaff399b"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="ece5ff15-7587-4abf-a02a-0bef46485079">Skills</span>&nbsp;<a class="tooltip-hover skill-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/using-ability-scores#Intimidation" data-tooltip-href="/skills/17-tooltip">Intimidation</a> +2</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="fd4a9030-eabe-4c0e-8cc6-86c7bf949dce"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="5cd73e91-194c-49b6-a506-f9e37ef979f2">Senses</span>&nbsp;passive Perception 10</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data" data-content-chunk-id="d8ef9770-7608-4b5c-a000-73ac1cee9df0"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="98dbb465-9e21-43c2-8503-0a59f38490e4">Languages</span>&nbsp;any one language (usually Common)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Data-Last" data-content-chunk-id="d5620c76-fe85-4ebf-b484-d88ec11c3c42"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="b105a825-dc0b-4b72-b5fc-6cdaf7ae58e4">Challenge</span>&nbsp;1/2 (100 XP)</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body-Last--apply-before-heading-" data-content-chunk-id="34bfae81-820e-421d-a86d-3289f22f962b"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="82bbdc95-601c-4d95-b18e-6b73d5d1330d">Pack Tactics.&nbsp;</span>The thug has advantage on an attack roll against a creature if at least one of the thug’s allies is within 5 feet of the creature and the ally isn’t <a class="tooltip-hover condition-tooltip" href="/compendium/rules/basic-rules/appendix-a-conditions#Incapacitated" data-tooltip-href="/conditions/7-tooltip">incapacitated</a>.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Heading" data-content-chunk-id="c1e104dd-81a5-4d00-9b08-0030d8d9dfb6">Actions</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="f0178e0c-2db7-422b-bc36-4657d18e010b"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="91aa1b72-f074-480b-b7f1-fc7072dabeda">Multiattack.&nbsp;</span>The thug makes two melee attacks.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="7b5370bf-188f-46b3-9ab2-302bfcd197f2"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="04280ed6-fb25-4c09-a043-98b0d29c08cf">Mace.&nbsp;</span><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="2d5e0047-ae39-4850-863a-d58250d41dc7">Melee Weapon Attack:</span>&nbsp;+4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one creature.&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="23c4745b-933a-4f31-9aa8-213b7f30887e">Hit:</span>&nbsp;5 (1d6 + 2) bludgeoning damage.</p>
<p class="Stat-Block-Styles_Stat-Block-Body" data-content-chunk-id="81b46725-27aa-4832-b895-6c9b4e94cb06"><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Inline-Subhead-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="c658e4cc-d07c-4618-97d5-648ae85e1118">Heavy Crossbow.</span>&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="8d7cf354-3939-4a84-9573-c9f2acf15cbc">Ranged Weapon Attack:</span>&nbsp;+2 to hit, range 100/400 ft., one target.&nbsp;<span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Italic-Sans-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="da558c67-cdc4-4c17-b7b4-8015462c5b7f">Hit:&nbsp;</span>5 (1d10) piercing damage.</p>
</div>
<p class="Core-Styles_Core-Body-Last--to-apply-extra-space-" data-content-chunk-id="be91704d-e641-482b-a666-33c9bda52d40"><span class="Serif-Character-Style_Bold-Serif" data-content-chunk-id="86c311a3-8f25-4df9-aa8c-f09e39e77655">Thugs</span>&nbsp;are ruthless enforcers skilled at intimidation and violence. They work for money and have few scruples.</p>
